the girl he has a crush on, the girl he's always had a crush on

AU Potterverse story.
Something's wrong. Harry and Hermione find themselves in a place that should be familiar, but there are too many things that don't ring true to what they think they know. Can they figure out what to do and who can they trust while they do it? More importantly, can they escape whole and come to terms with new information and the changes it brings?
